) male sternite VII; (
35
) postero-median portion of male sternite VII; (
36
) male sternite VIII; (
37-40
) aedeagus in lateral and in ventral view; (
41
) basal portion of dorsolateral apophysis in lateral view. Scale bars: 34, 36-41: 0.2 mm; 35: 0.1 mm.
